Text:
Thank you BiBi, I have no way to access releases or uploads from GreenyGaming, 

I checked their fb..etc and tried to access the website but it gave access denied. 

Is there a way for a Canadian to get their releases directly?

When they announced a new release on FB or Twitter, just search for the torrent file using Google. You should find some small torrent tracker on which they released it. Or wait till I find it and upload it on TPB :)
